Run this command in your terminal in the directory OpenShot was downloaded to verify the SHA256 checksum:
  echo "2ef8bc773b2ad8a6811cfdfd6d7187dc7e95a284a9f39033eac6675cf78eef2c  OpenShot-v3.4.0-x86_64.AppImage" | shasum -a 256 --check

You should get the following output:
  OpenShot-v3.4.0-x86_64.AppImage: OK